;Users on 64-bit Windows who download Firefox can get our 64-bit version by default. That means you get a more secure version of Firefox, one that also <a href="%(crashes)s">crashes a whole lot less</a>. How much less? In our tests so far, 64-bit Firefox reduced crashes by 39%% on machines with 4GB of RAM or more.
Uporabniki 64-bitnega sistema Windows, ki prenesejo Firefox, lahko privzeto prejmejo našo 64-bitno različico. To pomeni, da boste prejeli varnejšo različico Firefoxa, ki <a href="%(crashes)s">je stabilnejša</a>. Kako vemo? V dosedanjih testiranjih smo ugotovili, da 64-bitna različica Firefoxa zmanjša število sesutij za 39%% na napravah s 4 GB pomnilnika ali več.


